##
ABOUT EMCIEN (mCn)
##
Emcien does "automated pattern detection"

Abstract graph based-analytics, applied across several problem domains
- Graphs are a good abstraction for modeling connections between discrete pieces of data
  - Especially useful for analyzing unstructured, categorical, or text-based data
- The core product is novel (and proprietary)
- Peripheral code touches on well known graph ideas:
  - Shortest path
  - Page rank
  - Community detection (modularity)





















##
WHAT IT ISNT (EXACTLY) ...
##
- Machine learning
  - Tends to work with numerical data using tools from linear algebra
- Online analytical processing (OLAP)
  - Tends to entail traditional statistical methods and SQL queries





















##
THE TRANSITION
##
- "There exists" usually isn't sufficient
  - Except when looking for counterexamples
- Problems aren't usually posed formally
- Constant collaboration is key
- Engineering tradeoffs





















